      "content": "wait really?? do u have to go to the er for that? i dont have insurance that covers emergency visits well and i've had stuff like this happen before where it just went away after a day or two. maybe i should just try some ear drops or something and see if it clears up by tomorrow morning? seems like a lot of trouble for just a clogged feeling.",
