    "summary": "In this transcript, a user describes a sudden hearing loss following a \"pop\" in the ear and attempts to minimize the severity due to cost concerns. The assistant repeatedly identifies the situation as a potential medical emergency (perforated eardrum) and strongly advises the user to seek professional medical attention immediately while warning against self-treatment.",
